_sText: This is a fantasy fun Map. The Location is a Canyon Area. At the Start Terror Fraction has AK 47 and Deagle, the Counter Fraction has M4A1 and Deagle. I put a AWP on the highest Place. The Barrel Stations are explosive, so be carefull. There are 2 Hide Ways into the House. There are NAV Files into the Pack (made by chizbone) so you can play offline with BOTS. The BSP Files are into the Pack to, maybe you like to costum my Map ;) Map made by skillor NAV Files made by chizbone Have Fun
